title: Silveiro Garcia
text:
Silveiro Garcia (born 2 April 1994) is an <a href="East%20Timor">East Timor</a>ese <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who currently plays as a <a href="Forward%20%28association%20football%29">forward</a> for <a href="AS%20Ponta%20Leste">AS Ponta Leste</a> in <a href="Liga%20Futebol%20Amadora">Liga Futebol Amadora</a> and he also play for <a href="Timor-Leste%20national%20football%20team">Timor-Leste national football team</a>.
International career.
Garcia made his senior international debut in a 1–2 loss against <a href="Chinese%20Taipei%20national%20football%20team">Chinese Taipei</a> in a <a href="2019%20AFC%20Asian%20Cup%20qualification%20%E2%80%93%20Play-off%20Round">2019 AFC Asian Cup qualification</a> on 11 October 2016.
